The paper proposes a method for accurate delineation of skin lesions using deep learning techniques, specifically deep convolutional and recurrent neural networks. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. Additionally, the use of deep learning techniques indicates that the paper may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also deals with image retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM) applications, which further supports the likelihood of these sub-categories.
